msgid "Scenario I: Return to Curtain Call"
msgstr "冒险I：重返谢幕"

msgid ""
"Attach the Return to Curtain Call scenario reference card to the Royal Emissary. It gains the following text:\n"
"\"This card cannot be detached from Royal Emissary (even if Royal Emissary leaves play).\n"
"<b>Forced</b> - After Royal Emissary is added to the victory display: Place 1 resource on this card, as a warning.\n"
"For each warning on this card, Royal Emissary gets +1 [per_investigator] health."
msgstr ""
"将重返谢幕冒险辅助卡叠加到皇家密使。其获得以下文字：\n"
"“本卡牌不能从皇家密使解除叠加(即使皇家密使离场)。\n"
"<b>强制</b> - 在皇家密使加入胜利牌区后：在本卡牌上放置1资源，作为一个警告。\n"
"本卡牌上每有一个警告，皇家密使+1[per_investigator]生命值。”"

msgid "Construct the act deck using all six copies of Act 2a - \"The Stranger.\""
msgstr "使用全部六张场景2a——“陌生人”来组成场景牌堆。"

msgid "Alaran Mists"
msgstr "阿拉然迷雾"

msgid "Add 1 [cultist] and 1 [tablet] token to the chaos bag."
msgstr "在混乱袋中增加1个[cultist]标记和1个[tablet]标记。"

msgid "Under the City"
msgstr "城市之下"

msgid "Add 1 [cultist] and 1 [elder_thing] token to the chaos bag."
msgstr "在混乱袋中增加1个[cultist]标记和1个[elder_thing]标记。"

msgid "Here Is My Reply"
msgstr "这就是我的回答"

msgid "Add 1 [tablet] and 1 [elder_thing] token to the chaos bag."
msgstr "在混乱袋中增加1个[tablet]标记和1个[elder_thing]标记。"
